TI  - An integrated coastal zone observatory at municipal level: the case of Kavala Municipality, NE Greece
T2  - JOURNAL OF COASTAL CONSERVATION
LA  - English
KW  - ICZM Observatory
KW  - Coastal management and planning
KW  - Web-GIS
KW  - Operational numerical models
