TI  - Assessing poverty and livelihood vulnerability of the fishing communities in the context of pollution of the Churni River, India
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL SCIENCE AND POLLUTION RESEARCH
LA  - English
KW  - Water pollution
KW  - Churni River
KW  - Fishing economy
KW  - Coping strategy
