TI  - Assessment of indigenous farming practices of Nilotic Nuer farmers in Gambella region, south-west Ethiopia
T2  - JOURNAL OF AGRICULTURE AND ENVIRONMENT FOR INTERNATIONAL DEVELOPMENT
LA  - English
