TI  - Does anthropogenic upstream water withdrawal impact on downstream land use and livelihood changes of Teesta transboundary river basin in Bangladesh?
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL MONITORING AND ASSESSMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Land use
KW  - Livelihoods
