TI  - A systematic investigation of flood resilience measures in the Mekong River Basin
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL SCIENCE & POLICY
LA  - English
KW  - Flood resilience
KW  - Resilience measures
KW  - Literature analysis
KW  - Flood risk management
