TI  - Genotype x environment interaction analysis and climatic factors impacts on grain yield in rainfed durum wheat trials in Iran
T2  - BMC PLANT BIOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - AMMI
KW  - Climatic factors
KW  - Durum wheat
