TI  - Application of the Farm Simulation Model approach on economic loss estimation due to Coronavirus (COVID-19) in Bangladesh dairy farms-strategies, options, and way forward
T2  - TROPICAL ANIMAL HEALTH AND PRODUCTION
LA  - English
