TI  - Conservation agriculture-based wheat production better copes with extreme climate events than conventional tillage-based systems: A case of untimely excess rainfall in Haryana, India
T2  - AGRICULTURE ECOSYSTEMS & ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Conservation agriculture-based wheat production system
