TI  - Faidherbia albida trees form a natural buffer against millet water stress in agroforestry parklands in Senegal
T2  - BIOTECHNOLOGIE AGRONOMIE SOCIETE ET ENVIRONNEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Leaf water potential
KW  - interactions
KW  - yield
KW  - biodiversity
KW  - West Africa
