TI  - Nuts about trees? Tree quantity, species richness, and key species in smallholder agroforestry systems and their associations with groundnut (Arachis hypogaea) yields in Senegal
T2  - AGROFORESTRY SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - Agroforestry
