TI  - Smallholder Coffee in the Global Economy-A Framework to Explore Transformation Alternatives of Traditional Agroforestry for Greater Economic, Ecological, and Livelihood Viability
T2  - FRONTIERS IN SUSTAINABLE FOOD SYSTEMS
LA  - English
