FX  - Special thanks to H. Mitchell and P. Bassett for their instrumental role in initiating manta ray data collection through Aquatic Alliance and to the Lembongan Marine Association and local dive community for their generous support. We extend our appreciation to all MMF staff and volunteers, notably L. Ellevog, L. Auditore, A. Zeintrinanda, and M. Priadhi, for their invaluable assistance in data collection and processing. We also express gratitude to Y. Papastamatiou and J. Rehage for their insightful thesis feedback and to C. Rohner for the original CMR modelling 'R' codes. Additionally, we thank all citizen scientists who contributed photo-identification data and the MMF team and board for their unwavering administrative support throughout the project. This is contribution #1808 from the Institute of Environment at Florida International University.
