TI  - Subregional variation in cover and diversity of hard coral (Scleractinia) in the Western Province, Solomon Islands following an unprecedented global bleaching event
T2  - PLOS ONE
LA  - English
KW  - MARINE PROTECTED AREAS
KW  - CLIMATE-CHANGE
KW  - REEFS
KW  - RESILIENCE
KW  - RECOVERY
KW  - IMPACTS
