TI  - Can payments for ecosystem services secure the water tower of Tibet?
T2  - AGRICULTURAL SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - water conservation
KW  - hydrological model
KW  - ecosystem services
KW  - minimum data
KW  - CLIMATE
KW  - EFFICIENCY
