TI  - "My home garden is a peace maker": perceived impact pathways of a home gardening intervention in rural Kenya: the ALIMUS study
T2  - JOURNAL OF HEALTH POPULATION AND NUTRITION
LA  - English
KW  - Climate change
KW  - Agriculture
KW  - Home gardening
KW  - Perceptions
KW  - Qualitative
