TI  - Surge-flow alternate furrow irrigation for enhancing water productivity in semiarid regions
T2  - INDIAN JOURNAL OF AGRICULTURAL SCIENCES
LA  - English
KW  - Alternate furrow
KW  - Fennel
KW  - Semi-arid region
KW  - Surge flow
