TI  - Marine reserves help preserve genetic diversity after impacts derived from climate variability: Lessons from the pink abalone in Baja California
T2  - GLOBAL ECOLOGY AND CONSERVATION
LA  - English
KW  - Marine reserve
KW  - Overfishing
KW  - Restocking
KW  - Haliotis
