TI  - From Farms to Forests: An Exploration of Afforestation Efforts in Poland Under the Rural Development Programme (2007-2020)
T2  - SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - afforestation
KW  - private forests
KW  - land use change
KW  - rural development programme 2007-2013
