TI  - Addressing the challenges of agro-cattle farming in Bangladesh: A study on educated youth entrepreneurs
T2  - JOURNAL OF RURAL STUDIES
LA  - English
KW  - Agro-Cattle farming
KW  - Educated youth entrepreneurship
KW  - Livestock sector challenges
KW  - Theory of planned behavior
